                    <span>I think that this book is an excellent corporate finance book. If one person has difficulties understanding such a book written in a very clear language, then he or she better doesn't study finance or economics.The fact that the book is used as the required text for the corporate finance courses in the majority of the best business schools proves its importance.At the end of chapter problems are very useful too.Therefore one should also buy the solutions manual to check her own solutions. However I think that it would be perfect if these solutions were available in the book's website. </span>
                  
