                    <span>I am an MBA student with no financial background (having received my BS in a completely different field), this was the required text for my Corporate Finance class and it left me so confused I had to withdraw from the class so as not to ruin my GPA.  The text is of no value to students like myself that need to learn the basics in order to understand what the authors are talking about. Surely there's a better book out there somewhere for Professors to select for their students.</span>
                  
